                <p MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet1" class="Microcontent-Heading"><span class="Emphasis">How to Purchase Seats or Storage Space</span>
                </p>
                <ol>
                    <li>At the top of Central, click your user name, then <span class="Emphasis">Settings</span>.</li>
                    <li>At the top of the dialog, click <span class="Emphasis">License</span>.</li>
                    <li>On the left, select <b>Billing</b> and enter your credit card information, and click <b>Save</b>.</li>
                    <li>On the left, select <b>General</b>. Then to the right of the <b>Storage</b>, <b>Authors</b>, or <b>Subject Matter Experts</b> fields, enter a number to add. (Storage can be added in 10 GB increments.)</li>
                    <li>Click <b>Continue</b>.</li>
                    <li>Click <b>Purchase</b> and <b>OK</b>.</li>
                </ol>
